data.description: Welcome to this sunny, welcoming, open floor plan, hosting an abundance of opportunity. This 3 bedroom, 2 bath pool home is a prime example of what Merritt Island living is about. Beautiful and quiet neighborhood with a tremendous amount of community pride; go from the driveway to the beach in under ten minutes. The kitchen features a GAS range, newer appliances and breakfast nook. Separate indoor laundry room situated beside a beautiful and clean garage. High ceilings make this house feel like a home. Over the years, a loving homeowner has thoughtfully maintained this home. AC Unit: 2019, New Roof: 2017.  All screen around pool deck, floor to ceiling is BRAND NEW. Pool features a newer electric water heater. Don't miss the opportunity to stake your claim of beautiful Island Crossings!
